{"tid":2342741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】北 京 市委書記宣布 各區都進入「緊急狀態」","createTime":"2020-12-27T11:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T00:00:20.000Z","uid":293677,"like":317,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd473c4d709fe1f9f72579782484177f7fe7e4a","tid":2342741,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\">武漢肺炎》中國北京疫情再起 蔡奇：各區進入緊急狀態</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/27/phpcicKq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2FphpcicKq1.jpg&h=e2136d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020/12/27 18:02<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國北京週日（27日）連續第4天傳出武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）本土傳播的病例，由於擔心春節期間的返鄉與出遊的人潮可能導致病例激增，北京市官方已下令加強防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">中國共產黨北京市委書記蔡奇下令，封鎖住宅區和發現有人染病的村莊，並且宣布北京各區都進入「緊急狀態」。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n北京順義區目前正進行「重點區域大範圍篩檢」，計畫篩檢人數達80萬人。毗鄰順義的朝陽區已經完成了23萬人的測試，<span class=\"red\"><ins><span class=\"x-large\">沒有任何人呈陽性</span></ins></span>。朝陽區政府表示，未收到篩檢結果的人不得外出。此外，通州區的居民則是減少出入次數，加強量測體溫。<br />\n<br />\n中國少數城市，仍有零星的病例重演。中國官媒《環球時報》稱，當局計畫從2月11日起為期一週的農曆新年假期之前，對5000萬高風險族群施打疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n北京已要求其公務員從1月1日起至假日休假，並要求民眾避免不必要的旅行。主題公園和教堂等公共場所已減少了營業時間，北京的天主教堂、王府井天主教堂，已經停止信徒前往參拜，並停止了團體活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3393734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3393734&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=ea15998a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3393734&h=2bb2befe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3393734</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">中国明明已經清零 哪有武漢肺炎！<br />\n蔡奇惡意造謠！別有用心！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cadbb7f9a001bde1920f65bc230ba20f7a972c8f","tid":2342741,"uid":82640,"like":249,"dislike":5,"score":244,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n大陸成日喺度自吹自擂好撚巴閉<br />\n少少事就即刻要封晒城唔俾人出唔俾人入<br />\n<br />\n如果咁撚樣擾民無日安寧都叫成功抗疫<br />\n希特拉搞集中營直頭係優良規劃啦<br />\n<br />\n香港地反而就真係食玩買行山生活自如啦<br />\n係得個比共產黨控制嘅政府自己喺度唔撚知做乜"},{"pid":"811cd721fb222691b8dee54b068330401e16e833","tid":2342741,"uid":293677,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">完成了23萬人的測試，沒有任何人呈陽性。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然無人中招，做乜搞到咁大陣仗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e88dc9082903ca13d63cb9f7576d48c81f681e6","tid":2342741,"uid":82640,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"811cd721fb222691b8dee54b068330401e16e833","tid":2342741,"uid":293677,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">完成了23萬人的測試，沒有任何人呈陽性。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然無人中招，做乜搞到咁大陣仗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"從來都只係扮冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cbeaaec4542bc8f944eb5f24c7d9f7b94f61e4","tid":2342741,"uid":175540,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"咩春都戰時緊急狀態on99"},{"pid":"045968f349782e9bb2849d4a96b7abcb903eec29","tid":2342741,"uid":82640,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"f5cbeaaec4542bc8f944eb5f24c7d9f7b94f61e4","tid":2342741,"uid":175540,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"咩春都戰時緊急狀態on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"雞蛋殼國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf9e95929a1404050b5c90463b1d54c38ee33ae","tid":234